    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat. While it runs and drives reliably, it may require some minor upcoming maintenance, such as new brake pads or a tune-up, to keep it in peak operating shape. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone looking for affordable transportation.",
      "price": 20000.0,
